{"tid":2372961,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓美女YouTuber被批辱華 堅持泡菜是韓國文化：寧願不在中國活動","createTime":"2021-01-20T05:59:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T06:33:14.000Z","uid":16659,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1948a8e54d42c8df12ffe384c25b67ef4b7a3b14","tid":2372961,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T05:59:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_f9HvFiqk0QdwvTrzrWUBdYATno=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QPEYNACFBJBPRLBEYS7S2OYMLQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_f9HvFiqk0QdwvTrzrWUBdYATno%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQPEYNACFBJBPRLBEYS7S2OYMLQ.jpg&h=c1cc60b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n韓國人氣吃播YouTuber Hamzy，早前紅到去大陸，獲大陸平台簽約成為直播主，但近日疑因讚好了批評大陸人的留言，令大陸網民玻璃心碎一地，指她「辱華」。<br />\n<br />\n道歉後仍被解約<br />\n雖然Hamzy隨即在微博上道歉，指自己尊重大陸的飲食文化，不過此舉引起韓國網民不滿，Hamzy就向韓國fans表示：「因為大陸人一直罵，所以經理人公司要求我道歉，我當然認為泡菜、包飯是我國的文化。」而與Hamzy簽了合約的大陸平台，早前就發聲明宣佈與Hamzy解約及刪除所有Hamzy的影片，表示：「工作人員發現Hamzy在未告知本公司的情況下，擅自對傷害中國fans的言論進行回覆，這再次嚴重傷害了中國fans的情感以及我們公司對她的信任，公司堅決反對任何的辱華行為，也堅決不允許所簽署的外國博主有任何辱華的態度及言論，堅決維護我們國家和民眾的尊嚴，不允許任何形式的侵犯。」<br />\n<br />\n泡菜文化引爭議<br />\n對於公開道歉後仍被解約，昨日Hamzy就於YouTube頻道上寫下長文表明自己的立場，坦言：「如果為了要在中國活動就說泡菜是中國的，那我就不在中國活動了。」<br />\n<br />\nHamzy表示會道歉是因為讚好了的留言內容，的確有可能因為用字造成不愉快，她從頭到尾都是針對這一點而道歉。不過大陸方面把輿論牽扯到泡菜文化是哪個國家一事，Hamzy表示：「現在起要講我的講法，如果中國人感到被背叛和生氣，是因為誤會我同意了貶低中國人的留言，那我認為我是該道歉的，不管是甚麼原因都是在我頻道上發生的，這也是對喜愛支持我的人的道義和禮儀。但如果為了要在中國活動就得說泡菜是中國的，那我就不在中國活動了，中國人也不需要為了在韓國活動就說中國食物是韓國食物，這部份我想中國人都會理解的。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/cMyWqCCCSE_O4WGrdNq8FzaqZWI=/802x420/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NDM3TCUWPBDVXABDETYA2BNBGQ.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FcMyWqCCCSE_O4WGrdNq8FzaqZWI%3D%2F802x420%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNDM3TCUWPBDVXABDETYA2BNBGQ.JPG&h=1a8cd5ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/R4W5YPJDWBlktTTiwkQIIScpJ0A=/802x836/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PIN3QZKV3FF3LBBAQC7C3YTC2U.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FR4W5YPJDWBlktTTiwkQIIScpJ0A%3D%2F802x836%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPIN3QZKV3FF3LBBAQC7C3YTC2U.JPG&h=0987b8db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210120/U4KLISMVENDV5GB3DUKQODBXYA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210120%2FU4KLISMVENDV5GB3DUKQODBXYA%2F&d=CthjHxCXz%2Bl0vOF3eBkmerTKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=122c472c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210120%2FU4KLISMVENDV5GB3DUKQODBXYA%2F&h=5fd3dc0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210120/U4KLISMVENDV5GB3DUKQODBXYA/</a>"},{"pid":"574379228138df73ae70da4b1f5d100678a6ae77","tid":2372961,"uid":229026,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T06:00:45.000Z","msg":"只有肺炎不是中國的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cf9b78ca428a19c56300b583d112b7d9f943bd9","tid":2372961,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T06:02:40.000Z","msg":"食野個張相成個呀嬸咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffd4e35d67f7e0bb9c062f297bff6754786a3a84","tid":2372961,"uid":56701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T06:30:18.000Z","msg":"屌你老母咁都要搶...人地泡菜成個整法根本同中國啲咸酸菜唔撚同!"},{"pid":"0550f6215bb4eb82babcab1c90995eacbac6c27e","tid":2372961,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T06:31:35.000Z","msg":"美女?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0b8fc6c4cfbc324bd09a3ab905724fc0436146a","tid":2372961,"uid":170229,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T06:33:14.000Z","msg":"衡量過後都係決定做本土市場，算係咁。"}]}